4.  **Additional Services:** Any other relevant enhancement services that might benefit an executive with an active international lifestyle and family.

Please provide detailed cost breakdowns (monthly/annually) for each proposed insurance type and any additional services. The client aims to finalize new policies by late 2024.

Thank you.

